2052
01:07:19,450 --> 01:07:20,630
Do you think he's the one leaving?

2053
01:07:21,120 --> 01:07:22,470
It depends on what Yan thinks.

2054
01:07:23,120 --> 01:07:24,910
But what if it's a

2055
01:07:25,150 --> 01:07:26,150
surprise upset?

2056
01:07:27,280 --> 01:07:28,120
Guanjie is out.

2057
01:07:28,450 --> 01:07:29,710
(Chen Yijia & Ding Wanning's room)
So nervous.

2058
01:07:29,710 --> 01:07:30,710
Are you nervous?

2059
01:07:31,120 --> 01:07:32,280
I'm really scared.

2060
01:07:32,280 --> 01:07:33,280
How did your date

2061
01:07:33,280 --> 01:07:33,840
with Guanjie go?

2062
01:07:34,200 --> 01:07:34,760
It was okay.

2063
01:07:35,190 --> 01:07:36,560
Do you think he likes you?

2064
01:07:36,560 --> 01:07:37,390
Hard to tell.

2065
01:07:37,390 --> 01:07:37,950
He's still

2066
01:07:37,950 --> 01:07:38,910
attentive to Yan after he got back.

2067
01:07:39,360 --> 01:07:41,120
(Zhu Huiyan & Yang Tinghong's room)
Kind of nervous.

2068
01:07:41,120 --> 01:07:43,470
What am I nervous about?

2069
01:07:43,470 --> 01:07:44,430
Can someone tell me?

2070
01:07:44,500 --> 01:07:46,820
(Yang Tianyu & Wu Guanjie's room)

2071
01:07:46,840 --> 01:07:47,840
Today's been great.

2072
01:07:48,000 --> 01:07:50,080
(Liu Jiayi & Wu Yihan's room)
Will this add points for Yanting?

2073
01:07:50,670 --> 01:07:51,120
Yeah.

2074
01:07:51,520 --> 01:07:52,830
What's the score between them now?

2075
01:07:53,870 --> 01:07:54,360
I can't take it.

2076
01:07:54,950 --> 01:07:56,230
I haven't even started...

2077
01:07:56,230 --> 01:07:57,840
I haven't started
thinking about that.

2078
01:07:57,840 --> 01:07:59,120
Then how did you cast your vote?

2079
01:08:00,300 --> 01:08:01,540
(Huang Jiawei & Lu Yanting's room)

2080
01:08:01,560 --> 01:08:02,870
I'm packing my stuff right now.

2081
01:08:03,360 --> 01:08:04,230
Bro.

2082
01:08:06,120 --> 01:08:07,520
Hey man.

2083
01:08:07,910 --> 01:08:08,870
Just stay here.

2084
01:08:09,670 --> 01:08:10,190
Keep it up.

2085
01:08:10,650 --> 01:08:12,080
I think I should be the one leaving.

2086
01:08:12,080 --> 01:08:13,390
I don't have anyone else

2087
01:08:13,390 --> 01:08:15,470
to get to know on the island.

2088
01:08:15,470 --> 01:08:16,270
No feelings left

2089
01:08:16,270 --> 01:08:17,720
for anyone.

2090
01:08:18,350 --> 01:08:19,560
So I'm ready.

2091
01:08:19,560 --> 01:08:20,750
I think I should go.

2092
01:08:26,160 --> 01:08:27,470
After spending the day together,

2093
01:08:27,470 --> 01:08:29,270
I believe Jiayi's balance

2094
01:08:29,270 --> 01:08:30,200
is leaning toward me.

2095
01:08:30,600 --> 01:08:31,830
Of course I was hoping Jiayi

2096
01:08:31,830 --> 01:08:33,350
would give me her full vote.

2097
01:08:36,910 --> 01:08:37,950
I'm a little worried,

2098
01:08:37,950 --> 01:08:39,270
but honestly, not that much.

2099
01:08:39,270 --> 01:08:41,040
I still have pretty
strong faith in myself.

2100
01:08:41,040 --> 01:08:41,950
The day before,

2101
01:08:41,950 --> 01:08:43,680
when Jiayi and I went on that date,

2102
01:08:43,680 --> 01:08:44,470
I could tell

2103
01:08:44,470 --> 01:08:46,000
she was genuinely happy.

2104
01:08:46,000 --> 01:08:46,270
Yeah.

2105
01:08:47,000 --> 01:08:47,720
You never know.

2106
01:08:48,000 --> 01:08:49,680
Maybe Charlie will get all in.

2107
01:08:49,680 --> 01:08:50,520
That'd be hilarious.

2108
01:08:51,520 --> 01:08:52,560
That'd be too funny.

2109
01:08:54,120 --> 01:08:55,830
I'm scared Xuan Cheng
might get eliminated.

2110
01:08:56,300 --> 01:08:58,080
(Liu Jiayi & Wu Yihan's room)
I only told you...

2111
01:08:58,080 --> 01:08:58,910
When it was a choice

2112
01:08:58,910 --> 01:08:59,750
between two people,

2113
01:08:59,750 --> 01:09:00,600
the other name was

2114
01:09:00,600 --> 01:09:01,430
Xuan Cheng.

2115
01:09:01,430 --> 01:09:02,160
I'm really nervous.

2116
01:09:02,160 --> 01:09:03,310
One vote is the lowest.

2117
01:09:03,870 --> 01:09:04,450
There's also Jiawei.

2118
01:09:05,040 --> 01:09:06,080
So what do we do?

2119
01:09:08,310 --> 01:09:10,720
Who's leaving today?

2120
01:09:11,350 --> 01:09:13,240
How could Xuan Cheng be the one to go?

2121
01:09:13,240 --> 01:09:14,160
It doesn't make sense.

2122
01:09:14,160 --> 01:09:15,200
I think the person who leaves

2123
01:09:15,200 --> 01:09:16,600
is the one no one likes.

2124
01:09:17,080 --> 01:09:17,870
Based on the game rules,

2125
01:09:17,870 --> 01:09:19,310
isn't that the logic here?

2126
01:09:19,310 --> 01:09:19,640
Right?

2127
01:09:20,080 --> 01:09:21,120
Not necessarily.

2128
01:09:21,120 --> 01:09:22,160
Then how should I cast my vote?

2129
01:09:22,160 --> 01:09:23,520
I don't have enough…

2130
01:09:23,520 --> 01:09:24,790
Then pick the one you truly like.

2131
01:09:25,350 --> 01:09:26,470
Just go with your feelings.

2132
01:09:27,080 --> 01:09:28,240
If both stay, that'd be ideal.

2133
01:09:28,830 --> 01:09:29,430
If…

2134
01:09:29,430 --> 01:09:30,750
One ends up leaving without staying.

2135
01:09:30,750 --> 01:09:32,270
That's the answer you were hoping for.

2136
01:09:32,720 --> 01:09:33,720
You're making me tear up here.

2137
01:09:34,000 --> 01:09:34,560
Don't cry.

2138
01:09:34,560 --> 01:09:35,390
You cry, I cry too.

2139
01:09:36,430 --> 01:09:38,310
I never even thought about that.

2140
01:09:38,310 --> 01:09:39,000
Now I feel like

2141
01:09:39,000 --> 01:09:40,310
no one's voting for him.

2142
01:09:40,310 --> 01:09:41,430
Everyone else has someone.

2143
01:09:41,430 --> 01:09:43,560
But for him, there's no chance at all.

2144
01:09:43,560 --> 01:09:44,750
The most he could get is one vote.

2145
01:09:47,520 --> 01:09:49,350
I can't let him leave.

2146
01:09:50,180 --> 01:09:51,740
(Delivery finished)

2147
01:09:51,750 --> 01:09:55,000
Tonight's delivery of affection is done.

2148
01:09:55,000 --> 01:09:56,520
All Island residents,

2149
01:09:56,520 --> 01:09:58,910
please gather at the Square.

2150
01:09:59,200 --> 01:10:00,040
Who's

2151
01:10:00,520 --> 01:10:01,080
leaving today?

2152
01:10:01,430 --> 01:10:01,950
Okay.

2153
01:10:01,950 --> 01:10:02,430
Time to go.

2154
01:10:03,640 --> 01:10:04,160
Time to go.

2155
01:10:04,900 --> 01:10:05,270
Let's go.

2156
01:10:06,000 --> 01:10:07,000
Seriously?

2157
01:10:07,000 --> 01:10:07,750
Stop joking.

2158
01:10:08,040 --> 01:10:08,470
It's fine.

2159
01:10:08,470 --> 01:10:09,160
Let's not overthink.

2160
01:10:09,160 --> 01:10:09,680
Exactly.

2161
01:10:15,560 --> 01:10:16,160
So nervous.

2162
01:10:16,750 --> 01:10:17,470
Why are you nervous?

2163
01:10:23,830 --> 01:10:24,390
Cold, Han?

2164
01:10:25,350 --> 01:10:25,910
Not really.

2165
01:10:25,910 --> 01:10:26,310
It's fine.

2166
01:10:37,470 --> 01:10:38,680
Islanders,

2167
01:10:38,680 --> 01:10:39,790
unfortunately,

2168
01:10:39,790 --> 01:10:41,640
in tonight's choice round,

2169
01:10:41,950 --> 01:10:43,870
those with the lowest weight scores...

2170
01:10:48,870 --> 01:10:49,910
There were two.

2171
01:10:50,640 --> 01:10:51,470
What?

2172
01:10:53,680 --> 01:10:54,200
What?

2173
01:10:54,200 --> 01:10:55,000
Now,

2174
01:10:55,240 --> 01:10:57,310
the islander with
the highest weight score,

2175
01:10:57,310 --> 01:10:58,240
Liu Jiayi.

2176
01:10:58,240 --> 01:10:59,950
Please head to the balance zone.

2177
01:10:59,950 --> 01:11:01,870
Pick someone to save.

2178
01:11:12,350 --> 01:11:12,950
You okay?

2179
01:11:14,000 --> 01:11:14,520
No, I'm not.

2180
01:11:21,170 --> 01:11:23,470
WeTV "Live and Love S2"

2181
01:11:23,470 --> 01:11:25,180
will pause updates
from Feb 16 for a week.

2182
01:11:25,180 --> 01:11:27,000
Regular updates resume Feb 23.

2183
01:11:27,000 --> 01:11:29,510
Spring Festival Special Project
launches Feb 16.

2184
01:11:29,510 --> 01:11:31,860
Islanders on Balance Island
are spending the New Year with you.

2185
01:11:31,860 --> 01:11:34,180
Plus surprise livestreams

2186
01:11:34,190 --> 01:11:35,820
throughout Spring Festival.

2187
01:11:35,860 --> 01:11:36,560
(Preview)

2188
01:11:36,560 --> 01:11:37,600
Gentle Head Chef

2189
01:11:38,310 --> 01:11:39,240
is about to show up.

2190
01:11:40,120 --> 01:11:40,790
Let me take a bite.

2191
01:11:44,830 --> 01:11:45,720
Sure.

2192
01:11:45,720 --> 01:11:50,430
♪Give your whole life to me♪

2193
01:11:51,950 --> 01:11:53,430
Your are like "Oh" and "Wow".

2194
01:11:53,430 --> 01:11:54,310
I'm a puppy now.

2195
01:11:56,830 --> 01:11:57,680
Procured.

2196
01:11:57,910 --> 01:11:59,000
Bye bye. See you.

2197
01:11:59,000 --> 01:12:02,040
♪You'll always be my baby♪

2198
01:12:02,040 --> 01:12:03,200
♪Baby♪

2199
01:12:03,200 --> 01:12:04,470
Keep looking at me like that,

2200
01:12:04,470 --> 01:12:06,080
and we'll be the ones

2201
01:12:06,080 --> 01:12:06,910
singing Marry Me Today.

2202
01:12:06,910 --> 01:12:07,470
Yang.

2203
01:12:11,900 --> 01:12:13,270
(February 11, 12 pm)
Let's play word guessing.

2204
01:12:13,280 --> 01:12:14,220
(Pursue love on Balance Island)
Is it a person?

2205
01:12:14,270 --> 01:12:14,660
(Ex-girlfriend)
Yes.

2206
01:12:14,660 --> 01:12:15,240
(Mother-in-law)
Person?

2207
01:12:15,350 --> 01:12:15,680
Yes.

2208
01:12:15,750 --> 01:12:16,200
(Hunk)
Person?

2209
01:12:16,430 --> 01:12:16,640
Yes.

2210
01:12:16,790 --> 01:12:17,200
Person?

2211
01:12:17,220 --> 01:12:17,830
(Cast-wide trend)

2212
01:12:17,830 --> 01:12:18,240
Yes.

2213
01:12:18,820 --> 01:12:19,470
(Again; Flag raising ceremony)
Person?

2214
01:12:19,790 --> 01:12:20,640
No.

2215
01:12:20,660 --> 01:12:22,100
(I'm just different)

2216
01:12:22,160 --> 01:12:23,600
Aren't you two
standing way too close?

2217
01:12:23,600 --> 01:12:25,430
There's literally
no space to get in.

2218
01:12:25,430 --> 01:12:26,470
They're doing it
on purpose.

2219
01:12:26,470 --> 01:12:26,910
Fixed the game.

2220
01:12:26,910 --> 01:12:27,680
On purpose.

2221
01:12:29,240 --> 01:12:30,270
Do you ever feel like…

2222
01:12:30,270 --> 01:12:32,040
You can actually
get results on the island?

2223
01:12:33,680 --> 01:12:34,240
What about you?

2224
01:12:35,240 --> 01:12:37,430
Something really surprised me.

2225
01:12:37,430 --> 01:12:38,120
It was yesterday,

2226
01:12:38,120 --> 01:12:39,520
I was the one who almost left.

2227
01:12:39,640 --> 01:12:41,080
If it really doesn't work out,

2228
01:12:41,310 --> 01:12:42,080
then forget it.

2229
01:12:42,600 --> 01:12:43,600
Join my side.

2230
01:12:45,790 --> 01:12:46,560
Everyone.

2231
01:12:46,560 --> 01:12:48,540
(Happy New Year!)

2232
01:12:48,780 --> 01:12:49,500
(Woohoo!)

2233
01:12:49,720 --> 01:12:51,200
(Watch Live and Love with us)
Why not ask directly?

2234
01:12:51,200 --> 01:12:52,910
(on February. at 12 pm.)
Like they're off-topic.

2235
01:12:52,910 --> 01:12:55,040
He thought, "Fine, just wait."

2236
01:12:55,040 --> 01:12:56,790
One guy is about to leave.

2237
01:12:56,900 --> 01:12:58,000
(Shocked)

2238
01:12:58,000 --> 01:12:59,640
(Oh no)
Oh no.

2239
01:12:59,640 --> 01:13:00,520
This is bad.

2240
01:13:00,520 --> 01:13:02,270
(Love can't match brotherhood)
Sworn friends at last.

2241
01:13:03,350 --> 01:13:04,750
That stare between them.

2242
01:13:04,750 --> 01:13:06,120
(Feeling it)
My cheeks hurt from smiling.

2243
01:13:07,430 --> 01:13:09,080
This moment finally came.

2244
01:13:09,300 --> 01:13:12,060
(Crowd goes wild)

2245
01:13:12,160 --> 01:13:13,180
(Can't believe my ears)
What did I hear?

2246
01:13:13,180 --> 01:13:14,080
I'm feeling all heated up.

2247
01:13:14,270 --> 01:13:15,080
(Too intense)
Me too.

2248
01:13:15,430 --> 01:13:16,680
(Excitement keeps going)
Stay tuned

2249
01:13:16,680 --> 01:13:17,910
"Live and Love S2".

2250
01:13:17,910 --> 01:13:19,080
Every episode is a thrill.
